### ğŸ§  Orders of Magnitude Game
A card-based educational game designed to help audiences develop intuition about
orders of magnitude through comparisons across biology, physics and astronomy
(e.g. humans, neurons, ants, stars, molecules).

- Format: printable cards and rules recto (Item to sort) - verso (solution)
- Audience: general public kids (10+) and adults
- Goal: develop quantitative intuition in an interactive way

